The paper deals with a task related to natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV), specifically the disambiguation of verbs in images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP tasks. The paper also uses embeddings, which are commonly used in machine learning and deep learning, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of images and visual features also suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) tasks, which could place it in the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) category.
